Nigerian veteran singer, Charly Boy, has taken to social media to advise the National Leader of the All Progressive Congress (APC) and presidential aspirant, Bola Ahmed Tinubu, with regards to the forthcoming 2023 general elections.
The legendary music star who advised the Nigerian politician through his official Instagram page, stated that Bola Ahmed Tinubu has really tried for the country, adding that it is time for him to let the youths take over the office of the presidency.
Charly Boy further revealed that what Tinubu needs now is to sleep and rest the way he is resting now, adding that a king maker must not become a king and he will pay him a visit one day.
